data.description: Spacious Family Home located in beautiful LaBelle Florida!  Built in 2019, this very well maintained 3 bedroom home offers a open concept floor plan with great room and 9' 4" ceiling height.  The kitchen features plenty of cabinet storage, separate pantry, large island with bar seating, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  The floor plan features sliding glass doors from the master bedroom and living room which lead out to the covered open lanai and privacy fenced back yard.  The three car garage is the perfectly set up with sealed garage coated flooring and plenty of space for storage.  Convent location close to schools, with easy access to Hwy 80, just minutes from town.  LaBelle is located approx. 25 minutes east of Fort Myers and 1.5 hour drive to east coast Miami/Lauderdale area.
